                     Margreten</rs></rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">verkauft worden war</triggerstring>.</rs>
            </p></div><div type="seal"><p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_I_1276">Besiegelt mit den Siegeln: 1. <rs type="person" ref="pe__georg_von_nikolsburg_QGW_II_I_1010"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Jorigen von Nicolspurg, des <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">rats</roleName> der stat ze Wienn</rs>, 2. <rs type="person" ref="pe__friedrich_dietram_QGW_II_I_1026"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Fridreichs des Dietrams, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">purger</roleName> daselbens</rs>.</rs></p></div><div type="nota"><p/></div><div type="lists"><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/placeList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/personList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/eventList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/orgList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/></div></body></text></TEI>